

getmoz - version 1.1

getmoz will download and install Mozilla nightly builds while archiving 
your old nightly and keeping your current plugins/searchplugins intact.



DIRECTIONS

To install getmoz, at a command prompt, type the following:
	su root
      	cd getmoz-1.1
      	chmod a+x install.sh
      	./install.sh

Once installed, to run getmoz, as a normal user at a command prompt, type the following:
        getmoz

To uninstall getmoz, at a command prompt, type the following:
	su root
      	cd getmoz-1.1
      	chmod a+x uninstall.sh
      	./uninstall.sh


